summary:
Expert on democratic innovations and civic technologies for more than 10 years, after several positions within local or national institutions and strong commitments to citizen-driven politics in France and Europe.
Today with Open Source Politics we help more than 200 clients to launch great participatory processes based on the Decidim digital platform.
headline: Co-founder & General Manager @ Open Source Politics || Civic tech expert

experience.description:
We provide open source #civictech platforms and high-level counsulting to cities, public institutions, companies and nonprofit engaging in participatory democracy.

More than 200 clients: European Commission, French National Assembly, French Senate, French Climate Convention, French Court of Accompts, Federal State of Belgium, Regions and Departments, cities (Bordeaux, Lille, Toulouse, Marseille, Nanc…) New York City, several political movements, Decathlon, EDF, Emmaüs, Greenpeace…
experience.title: Co-founder & General Manager
